    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Chop your <strong>leek[s]</strong> in half lengthways, wash thoroughly to remove any grit then top, tail and slice finely</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a little knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat and once hot, add the <strong>sliced leek </strong>and <strong>onion</strong> to the pan with your <strong>dried</strong> <strong>thyme </strong>and<strong> </strong>cook for 10-12 min or until softened</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ultimate-cheese-and-onion-cornish-pasty/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the leek softens, trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Once the leek and onion has softened, transfer to a medium bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>grated cheddar</strong>, your <strong>wholegrain mustard </strong>and <strong>soft cheese </strong>to the bowl with a generous grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>cheese & onion filling</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ultimate-cheese-and-onion-cornish-pasty/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>pizza base mix</strong> to a large bowl with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>vegetable oil </strong>and 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>warm water </strong>(you may not need all of it), a little at a time</p><p>Gently mix with a plastic spatula until a sticky dough ball has formed</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ultimate-cheese-and-onion-cornish-pasty/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Tip the <strong>dough</strong> out onto a floured work surface and cut into 1 per person</p><p>Roll each dough ball out to approx. 0.5cm thickness and 20cm wide with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Add the dough circle[s] to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Divide the <strong>cheese & onion filling </strong>evenly beween the <strong>dough circle[s]</strong>, covering only one half and leaving a border of dough clear around the edge</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ultimate-cheese-and-onion-cornish-pasty/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Fold the dough over the filled side of the dough circle[s] and press the edges together firmly with your fingers to seal in the mixture, with as little air trapped inside as possible</p><p>Pinch and roll the bottom edge up of the dough up and over the top edge, crimping the edges of the dough to seal \u2013 this is your <strong>pasty[ies]</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ultimate-cheese-and-onion-cornish-pasty/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-22 min or until the pastry is golden and cooked through \u2013 this is your <strong>ultimate</strong> <strong>cheese & onion Cornish pasty[ies]</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ultimate-cheese-and-onion-cornish-pasty/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the pasty[ies] are almost ready, boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>blanched peas</strong> to a pot, cover them with <strong>boiling water </strong>(just enough to cover them)</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 1 min or until they're warmed through</p><p>Once done, drain and return to the pot with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a little knob of <strong>butter</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/ultimate-cheese-and-onion-cornish-pasty/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>ultimate</strong> <strong>cheese & onion Cornish pasty </strong>with the <strong>buttery peas </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
